                        <summary/>           
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <title ref="LIT7321InfantsSus"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> 
                                ጸሎት፡ በእንተ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">፡</supplied> ሱስንዮስ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው፡ ነባቢ፡ ወተናጋሪ፡
                                ጸሎት፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሱስንዮ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ስ፡</supplied> በእንተ፡ አሰስሎ፡ ደዌ፡ እምሕፃናት፡ እለ፡
                                ይጠብው፡ ጥበ፡ እምኵሉ፡ ደዌያት፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>  
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <title>Prayers against haemorrhage</title><!-- Issue #3237 -->
                            <note>Separated from the preceding prayer by a horizontal line. Defined as six independent prayers by 
                                <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1976Catalogue"/><citedRange unit="item">38</citedRange>
                                <citedRange unit="page">116–117</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1">
                                <title ref="LIT7767PPAlef"/>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ዓርጋዔ፡ ደም፡ አሌፍ፡ አሌፍ፡ አሌፍ፡ አልፋዋ፡ አልፋዋ፡ አልፋዋ፡
                                        </incipit>  
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
                                <title ref="LIT7768PPLisAflis"/>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሊስ፡ አፍሊስ፡ መሊ፡ ወመለሊስ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ከማሁ፡ አርግዕ፡ ደማ፡ ወአቁም፡ 
                                    ፍሬ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">፡</supplied> በማኅፃና፡ ለአመትከ፡ <gap reason="lost"/>
                                        </incipit>  
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.3">
                                <title ref="LIT7769PPNegus"/>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">እግዚአብሔር፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወእጉሥ፡ ዘፈኖከ፡ ላቲ፡ ለሔዋን፡ ፲፪ መላእክተ፡ ዑቃቤ፡ ከመ፡ ይእቀብዋ፡ በመዋዕለ፡ 
                                    <sic>ጽንሣሃ፡</sic> እስከ፡ አመ፡ ትወልድ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ከመ፡ የኀብዋ፡ ውሉደ፡ አርግዕ፡ ደማ፡ ወአቁም፡ ፍሬ፡ በማኅፀኖ፡ 
                                    ለአመትከ፡ <gap reason="lost"/></incipit>  
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.4">
                                <title ref="LIT5823MagicPrayer">Wa-yǝkawwǝn kama ʿǝḍ ʾǝnta tǝklǝt ḫaba muḫaza māy</title>
                                <note>Magic prayer with an allusion to <ref cRef="betmas:LIT2000Mazmur.Ps1">Psalm 1:3</ref> and with some 
                                    variations to <ref type="mss" corresp="CJN001"/> or <ref type="mss" corresp="OMD002"/>.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወይከውን፡ ከመ፡ ዕፅ፡ እንተ፡ ትክልት፡ ኀበ፡ ሙኀዘ፡ ማይ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ከማሁ፡ ኢይትነገፍ፡ ፍሬ፡ 
                                    በማኅፀና<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">፡</supplied> ለአመትከ፡ <gap reason="lost"/></incipit>  
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.5">
                                <title ref="LIT7770PrAammen">Ba-salaśtu ʾakālāt wa-ba-ʾaḫadu malakot</title>
                                <note>Contrary to <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1976Catalogue"/><citedRange unit="item">38</citedRange>
                                    <citedRange unit="page">117</citedRange></bibl>, who defined <ref target="#ms_i2.5"/> as two separate prayers
                                    against vaginal haemorrhage. It contains <term key="MagicSymbols">magic glyphs (charaktêres)</term> towards the
                                    end.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> በ፫ አካላት፡ ወበ፩ መለኮት፡ አንተ፡ ጋኔን፡ ከመ፡ ኢትቅረብ፡ ኀበ፡ ሕፃና፡ 
                                    <gap reason="ellipsis"/> በስመ፡ አብ፡ አአምን፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ከመ፡ ኢትቅረበኒ፡ ወኢትልክፈኒ፡ አንተ፡ ሹቶላይ፡ ይልሳሕ፡ 
                                    ህምዘከ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">፡</supplied> <gap reason="ellipsis"/> በዝንቱ፡ አስማት፡
                                    ወበዝንቱ፡ ጠልሰም፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> አምሐልኩክሙ፡ ሐተምኩክሙ፡ ወለጐምኩክሙ፡ አንትሙ፡ አጋንንት፡ 
                                    <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ከመ፡ ኢትቅረቡ፡ ኀበ፡ ነፍሳ፡ ወሕፃና፡ ወሥጋሃ፡ ለአመትከ፡ <gap reason="lost"/></incipit>  
                            </msItem>
                        </msItem>
